  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a large bowl, mix together almond paste, shio-cure seasoning, and red wine",
    "Add the grass-fed beef to the bowl and mix until just combined",
    "Form the beef mixture into 4 patties",
    "Place the patties on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper and bake for 15 minutes",
    "While the burgers are cooking, toast the brioche buns",
    "Assemble the burgers with mixed greens, sliced red onion, and vegan mayo",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy"
